## Laptop Security Basics {background-image="/assets/background1.png" background-size="cover"}

::: incremental
- **Enable full disk encryption**
- **Set up screen lock** with password
- **Auto-lock after inactivity**
- **Regular software updates**
:::

---

## Mobile Device Security {background-image="/assets/slide1.png" background-size="cover"}

::: incremental
- **Strong passcode or biometrics**
- **Enable find my device**
- **App permissions review**
- **Regular OS updates**
:::

---

## Campus Computer Safety {background-image="/assets/background1.png" background-size="cover"}

::: incremental
- **Always log out completely**
- **Don't save passwords**
- **Use private/incognito mode**
- **Check for shoulder surfing**
:::

---

## Physical Security {background-image="/assets/slide1.png" background-size="cover"}

::: incremental
- **Never leave devices unattended**
- **Use cable locks** in study areas
- **Secure storage** in dorms
- **Insurance** for expensive devices
:::

